                                        </span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="box-content-row">
                                        <span>
                                            LOA:  <span id="team-info-down-loa" style="float: right"> - </span>
                                        </span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="box-content-row">
                                        <span>
